node.text: Who else can’t wait for @the_musicfest 2022!? MusicFest is in Steamboat Springs Colorado. Ski/board for 4 days with Texas Country music concerts all over the mountain starting after lunch till late night every night. There like a dozen stages where greats play. Follow their acct to find out when online books open to buy tickets that include lodging, concert tickets, lift tickets, and ski rentals.. Sign ups are happening soon. They usually sell out in a few hours

node.text:
We have a Netflix show!! Watch the full trailer in my bio!! Six episodes release September 1. Please like and comment the YouTube video if you want. You can also go on Netflix and “add to my list” and click the bell. Thank you to anyone who’s ever watched a video we’ve made. Absolutely love what we do here at Rodeo Time and it’s a blessing to bring it to the world through Netflix. Lord willing you all approve the way we represented the industry. Not that I’m surprised they called me or anything. I mean after all, I am the greatest bull rider to ever walk the earth!
“How to be a cowboy” with Dale Brisby
